title: Missa Bay LLC Recalls Chicken Wrap Products Due To Misbranding and Undeclared Allergens
summary: WASHINGTON, Nov. 16, 2017 Missa Bay LLC, a Swedesboro, N.J. establishment, is recalling approximately 46 pounds of chicken wrap products due to misbranding and undeclared allergens, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today. The product contains peanut and soy...
impacted_products: •2-lb packages containing 4 8-oz. trays of “Fresh Prep’D brand Buffalo Style Ranch Wrap Kit” with a “USE BY” date of 11/21/17.
